snippet: In the Reelz movie “Delete,” a young man, a reporter, a hacker and an F.B.I. agent battle malevolent machines linked by the Web.
abstract: Neil Genzlinger reviews Reelz television movie Delete, starring Keir Gilchrist, Erin Karpluk and Ryan Robbins.
lead_paragraph: In the Reelz movie “Delete,” a young man, a reporter, a hacker and an F.B.I. agent battle malevolent machines linked by the Web.
